snippet.title: Dark Cloud - Part 1
snippet.description:
Norune Village and Divine Beast Cave.
I would've split the damn thing like....First dive...stop at "stuck" floor...Georama for event...Second dive...Georama Deux...BOSS...but I decided to just put it all as one.  Meh. -_-

Don't mind any LONG loadings and waiting on chests or Atla.  It is not fun trying to edit 34 hours of footage. -_-
